-- Syrian Colonel Among 151 Crossing Into Turkey, Anatolia Says
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-06-28T10:09:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/syrian-colonel-among-151-crossing-into-turkey-anatolia-says.html
A colonel and a lieutenant-colonel
in the Syrian military were among 151 Syrians who crossed the
border into  Turkey  last night seeking refuge, the state-run
Anatolia news agency reported today.  About 35,000 Syrians have fled to Turkey to escape the
violence in their country, and the number of military defections
has been increasing, Deputy Prime Minister Besir Atalay told
Anatolia yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
